snippet.title: Best VGM 1955 - Paladin's Quest II - Throne of the Immortals
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1233 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A3PE47hImMo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Paladin's Quest II / Lennus II (1996)
Throne of the Immortals
Kohei Tanaka
